### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.uk@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### List Jobs (requires token from login)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/jobs
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Create Job
POST http://localhost:8000/api/jobs
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Building Inspection",
  "description": "Comprehensive building safety inspection"
}

###

### Assign Job (replace 1 with actual job ID)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/jobs/1/assign
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduled_at": "2026-02-20 14:00"
}

###

### Complete Job (replace 1 with actual job ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/jobs/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assessment": "Building structure is sound. Minor repairs needed on north wall. All safety requirements met."
}
